  "text": "For protein preparation, cells were cultured in 75 cm 2 flasks at a density of 2 Â 10 5 cells/flask and treated with 1 mM celastrol. After 48 h celastrol treatment, samples of total cellular proteins were prepared as described above. 2-DE analysis and MALDI-TOF MS/MS were conducted as described in our previous reports. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Detailed information can be found in Supplementary Materials and Methods.",
